name: Rockefeller Collection
description:
A stationery set for the gentlemen.  Monograms and detailed vintage cars create a strong and sophisticated means of correspondence.   

Available Colors:
Polar
Slate
Dark Brown
Black 

Dimensions: 4" x 6"
Set of 20 cards.  Additional quantities in sets of 10 available.
Printed on heavy ivory or white 80lb cover stock
Paired with same color envelopes

name: Float Postcards
description:
This set of brightly colored hot air balloon postcards lets you write whatever floats your balloon!  

Dimensions: 4" x 6"

Printed on heavy ivory 80lb cover stock
Set of 14

name: 'Tailor' Wedding Invitation
description:
Make a statement with these modern wedding invitations, with a linen vellum cover stitched along the top.  A more economical value than a outer jacket, but just as classy!   

Dimensions: 5" x 7"

Printed on ivory 80lb card stock.  
Includes lined envelope.  

*Color of thread and envelope liner customizable to match wedding colors.*  

Minimum order of 50.

name: Nautical Christening
description:
Set the stage for a wonderful event with these whimisical, nautical inspired invitations.  The tea length size flat invitation card comes in a sea blue sleeve, wrapped in sailor's twine and adorned with an antiqued cooper anchor charm.  Optional matching response set and lined envelopes available.     

Dimensions: 4"w x 9 1/4"l

Price includes flat invitation card and matching envelope.

Minimum order of 50.
